items.name: Dwarika Ko Pranam Dwarikadheesh Ko Pranam
Shri Krishna Tumhi Vishnu Tumhi Adhbudh Maya Dhari - 2
Bhawna Jaisi Rahi Jeev Ke Maan Prabhu Murat Deen Tasi Nihari
Dhund Se Utri Jyoti Ki Rekha
Hum Charan Jan Shree Krishan Chandra Ki Vanshavali Bakhan Kare
Jai Mahakaal Param Pita Shambhu Namaste
Om Namah Shivay - Shiv Tandav Stotra
Dhol Dhamkao Bajao Nagada Vijayshri Ka Jhanda Kanhaiya Ne Gada
